.TH LOA-MARK-READ 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
mark read \- Mark a book as read
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> mark read
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author).
.TP
Sets read status to yes and updates completion timestamp.
.TP
If total pages are known, progress is set to full pages.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> mark read
